"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-snoop-dogg-dressage-charlote-dujardin-olympics-paris-2024-b2590730.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The Independent's journalism is supported by our readers.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.413496196362978e-45, \"text\": \"The Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn commission.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The US rapper, businessman and celebrity icon has become an unlikely figurehead for Paris 2024 and equestrian was his latest stop  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7625241162946694, \"rank\": 0.30482056108641625, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.057626184106047e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 443, \"end\": 453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9989113911269035, \"rank\": 0.0010897933188120307, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  It is not every day that you seeSnoop Doggbroughtto the verge of tearsby a dancing horse named Jagerbomb.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This wasdressageat its bonkers best asTeam GBbanked a fourth equestrian medal, taking bronzefrom the team grand prix.\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9989113911269035, \"rank\": 0.0010897933188120307, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop hasbecome an unexpected figureheadfor theOlympics, rarely out of sight for more than an hour thanks to US broadcaster NBC.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7625241162946694, \"rank\": 0.30482056108641625, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999998551493368, \"rank\": 1.2170544139937185e-07, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was never going to miss this one, such was his delight at the 'crip-walking' horses in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9747883985630349, \"rank\": 0.02583628381118218, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside Martha Stewart, the rapper took in the early stages of a gripping tussle for the medal positions that saw Germany beat Denmark by a single percentage point with a winning score of 235.790.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martha_Stewart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.4307837297139e-33, \"text\": \"Martha Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martha_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martha_Stewart\"}, {\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.5459255453141153, \"rank\": 0.6093808335004312, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9996547221414576, \"rank\": 0.0003453962745840851, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of Snoop's presence, Britain's Carl Hester said: \\\"I'd heard he was here.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9840941014500801, \"rank\": 0.016162637820819593, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1289, \"end\": 1300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Hester\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carl Hester\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Hester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Hester\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the talk was he's here, everyone has been looking for him on the camera.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's great that he's enjoying dressage and he's here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thespectre of the Charlotte Dujardin scandalwas lifted somewhat by a sparkling performance from Becky Moody and homebred Jagerbomb, who were last-minute replacements afterDujardin's withdrawal and suspension.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair played the role of pathfinders to perfection as they added a sizeable chunk to their personal best to lift Hester, whose test contained a significant error, and Charlotte Fry onto the podium.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1790, \"end\": 1796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4830049788451544e-14, \"text\": \"Hester\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\"}, {\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Fry\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Fry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Fry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Fry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The emergence of Moody and 'Bomber' as the great entertainers of the Games is remarkable given that Moody nearly sold him as a young horse because she found him boring, only stopping short of doing so on the advice of her sister Hannah.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their story is exactly the kind of salve required torebuild the ancient discipline's reputation.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was expecting a lovely 10-day holiday in France but this is quite a bit better in reality,\\\" joked Moody.\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2256, \"end\": 2262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8836113941186104, \"rank\": 0.05164125494714328, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did not have the pressure for a long period beforehand, it all happened quite quickly.\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There were definitely moments of extreme nausea but we carried on and the team around us have been incredible, I do not feel like they have put any pressure on us at all.\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The vast majority of my pressure comes from myself but luckily I had great support and my horse was amazing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the choice of name, Moody explained: \\\"I bred him 10 years ago and at that point in my life I might have been partial to a Jagerbomb.\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It suits him.\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Also, my grandad, who was called Norman, we all called him 'Bomb' for some reason.\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2880, \"end\": 2886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\", \"score\": 0.9999503534878111, \"rank\": 4.909572813210815e-05, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, it was a little bit of a homage to him as well as the alcoholic beverage.\\\"\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 3008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aged 57, Hester became the second-oldest British Olympic medallist of the post-war era, with only fellow equestrian legend Nick Skelton having been older when he reached the podium.\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3019, \"end\": 3025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4830049788451544e-14, \"text\": \"Hester\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\"}, {\"begin\": 3051, \"end\": 3058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.880095305690293, \"rank\": 0.1263075202507095, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3115, \"end\": 3125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9989113911269035, \"rank\": 0.0010897933188120307, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}, {\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Skelton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nick Skelton\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Skelton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Skelton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hesterfeels Dujardin's suspensionhas created an opportunity to showcase the strength in depth in British dressage.\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3290, \"end\": 3306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's really important that we have done that because of how much (Dujardin) won and contributed to the team,\\\" said Hester.\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3433, \"end\": 3439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4830049788451544e-14, \"text\": \"Hester\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think a lot of people felt that if she wasn't on the team we would not be successful.\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us face it, if the same people are on the team all the time, it's not the greatest inspiration for the kids coming up because most kids' dreams are Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That mentality means that Hester's seventh Games isvery likely to be his last as an athlete.\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB have already won two golds and two bronzes in equestrian with Fry among the leading contenders for individual honours tomorrow.\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3789, \"end\": 3796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9964222010182123, \"rank\": 0.0035906455673423883, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 3843, \"end\": 3853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9989113911269035, \"rank\": 0.0010897933188120307, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think we are probably expected to do better in the individual,\\\" said Hester.\", \"from\": 3926, \"to\": 4005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3998, \"end\": 4004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4830049788451544e-14, \"text\": \"Hester\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am still standing so I am going to have one more sleepless night and go for tomorrow.\\\"\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4095, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch every moment of the Olympic GamesParis 2024live only ondiscovery+, the streaming home of the Olympics  Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4257, \"end\": 4268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9532019604681814e-19, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"